value:
I can't get enough of the delicious
food here. Even though I ate so much
this morning, I'm already starving...

Adults always compliment my
appetite. At least at first...

I think it's time for me to eat. Magic
always makes me so hungry.

What? No, there's no reason to be
worried about me. Moving around
always makes me this hungry.

A cookie in my right hand...dried
sweet potato in my left. Help! I don't
know which one to eat first.

*sniff* I thought I smelled a feast...
When do you usually eat around
here?

You know what would make a great
reward? A snack...or two...or three...

I'm not picky. I'll eat anything once...
so long as it's edible.

I must be hungrier than I thought. Do
you have anything to eat?

For me? Thank you! But, you know,
I'd rather have something I can eat...

Hello. My name is...Ilyana. I'm
studying magic. I'm also starving...
Do you have anything I can eat?

I learned a new expression today.$k$p"Eat me out of house and home..." Do
you know what it means?$k$pIt means "to eat too much, without
doing anything to help in return."
That's what Commander Anna said.$k$pHer face was so red when she saw
me eating. She said there was a limit
to what she could spend on food.$k$pI hope that someday, I'll be the type
of adult who can eat in all the houses,
without anyone getting upset.
たあ…
とうっ
きゃっ…
力が…
Get out of my way...
...it's time to eat!
I'm sorry...
Give me your snacks!
Another cookie…
うふふ…
I'm...Ilyana... I'm studying magic...
Did you just push me? Give me a snack and I'll forgive you.
I wish I could run around and play with everyone, but...I get so hungry, and...
Grown-ups always say I'm not picky when it comes to food. Is that a good thing?
*sniff sniff* Do you smell something good?
The food in this castle is so delicious. And there's so much! I've never been this happy....
I guess I could share my snacks with you... but only a little bit.
Okay...
...starving...
Is there food this way?
